UML:TaggedValue.value: All-components schema for the SWE Service Model namespace.

No dependency on SWES Common Codes as the code lists defined in that package are all encoded as virtual dictionaries, so there is no need to let the XML Schema from SWE Service Model include the schema from the codes package (which is empty and therefore should not be included in the official schema package from SWES).
